Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: eighties movie trivia
des: If you say "Alexa play 80's Movie Trivia" you will be presented with 5 questions each with a choice of 5 answers. Alexa with read your choices of answers along with a corresponding number. Answer using the number that is associated with the correct answer. At the end of the 5 questions Alexa will tell you how many you answered correctly.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
